[Shi Yi]

99
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:22,630
Hello?

100
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:30,920
Miss Shi.

101
00:05:31,410 --> 00:05:32,700
Are you here for Professor Zhousheng?

102
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,320
He's having lunch

103
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,120
