528
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:26,720
Seriously, you and your witty tricks.

529
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,240
Let's take the stairs.

530
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,080
When I was a student,

531
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,120
