567
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:26,080
You took the initiative?

568
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,240
Yeah, you know me.

569
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:29,560
I am pretty straightforward.

570
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,920
I usually speak my mind.

571
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:35,080
