898
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,480
Try to persuade her.

899
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,820
She is like a child. I am helpless.

900
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:37,360
I will go pack up

901
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:38,920
