910
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,790
Your great-grandson.

911
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:21,480
Your great-grandson.

912
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:23,810
He's doing homework right now.

913
00:42:26,290 --> 00:42:29,920
