944
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:38,080
go there for our sake?

945
00:43:39,280 --> 00:43:40,960
Okay, okay.

946
00:43:40,960 --> 00:43:42,280
Let's get ready then.

947
00:43:45,200 --> 00:43:46,320
All right.

948
00:43:48,770 --> 00:43:51,240
